                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17830723-94-off430 t17830723-94-cd431"></join> last, and putting her in fear and danger of her life, and taking from her person, and against her will, two guineas, value 42 s. one half guinea, value 10 s. 6 d . and 7 s. in monies numbered
